pandamanagementsystem

Class employeesData

  • java.lang.Object
    • pandamanagementsystem.employeesData

  • public class employeesData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the data for an employee in a management system. It includes information such as the employee's ID, first name, last name, username, password, and role.
